flowchart LR
  %% Maple Shield V1 — High-level Architecture

  CAM[Camera /<br/>Video Source] --> PRE[Preprocess<br/>resize + normalize]
  PRE --> INF[Inference<br/>YOLOv8 ONNX]
  INF --> POST[Postprocess<br/>NMS + scale]
  POST --> TRK[Tracking<br/>IoU + smoothing]
  TRK --> VEL[Velocity<br/>vx, vy, speed]
  VEL --> RISK[Risk Engine<br/>motion-weighted]
  RISK --> OVL[Overlay<br/>box + label]
  OVL --> VID[overlay.mp4]

  CAM --> RAW[raw.mp4]
  RISK --> LOG[JSONL Logger<br/>detections.jsonl]
  LOG --> REPLAY[Replay Tool]
  RAW --> REPLAY
  REPLAY --> VIEW[Review /<br/>Debug]

  TRK --> LIFE[Lifecycle<br/>lifecycle.json]


